        <h1>FAQ</h1>
        <ul>
            <li><h2>Are you a non-profit organization?</h2><br>
                <p>Yes we are a non-profit organization based out of Toronto, Ontario, Canada. We are supported primarily through personal and corporate donations.  An application is being reviewed for Charity Status through the Canadian Revenue Agency.</p>
            </li>
            <li><h2>How do we audit the volunteer process and time spent?</h2>
                <p>We have a high level of trust in our users and the legitimacy of their gifts.  Therefore, there is no official audit process.  However, it is recommended that the user uploads a picture of them performing the act.  This is both a nice token and proof of completion for the receiver.</p>
            </li>
            <li><h2>How is this an impactful gift?</h2><br>
                <ul>
                    <li>Highly personalized</li>
                    <li>High value by donating personal resources</li>
                    <li>Proof of planning, effort and time spent</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><h2>Why does it ask for a donation at the end?</h2><br>
                <p>Although volunteering and acts of kindness go a long way, we want to maximize our own impact.  While you are in a giving mindset, we want you to consider making a small donation as well – every dollar has a BIG impact.</p>
            </li>
            <li><h2>Can we offer tax receipts for donations?</h2><br>
            <p>Yes, the Gift of Time will provide a tax receipt for all donations to registered charities over the amount of $20 made through the website.  Please note, the Gift of Time is not a charitable organization; although there is an option to make a donation in support of the website (which is highly appreciative), the Gift of Time cannot offer a tax receipt for any direct donations to the site.  However, all other donations made through the site over the amount of $20 to charities will provide a tax receipt.</p>
            </li>
            <li><h2>What will donations to the Gift of Time support?</h2><br>
            <p>All donations support the marketing efforts of the website.  It is our belief that by informing more people of this unique platform, we are promoting volunteering in the community and effectively creating volunteer hours that would have never been performed.  Therefore, your donation to the website creates additional volunteer hours to the macro and micro communities across the world.</p>
            </li>
